si eredm\'e9ny\'fcnket }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f0\fs22\insrsid4985011\charrsid5309908 integr\'e1lni}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs22\insrsid4985011\charrsid5309908  a r\'e9gebbi kutat\'e1si eredm\'e9nyekkel, s be kell 
